reviewText: Ok so ive only watched Rosario tijeras so far, but was blown away great movie set in Medellin Colombia. I was in Medellin last year and it brought back memories of a great city... Muy buena pelicula Rosario Tijeras, muestra mucho sobre Medellin Colombia, buenisimo la pelicula...
Item arrived promptly and in great condition, as was stated in the ad. Extremely happy with purchase and seller.
